Older individuals receiving tofacitinib as induction and maintenance therapy to treat UC may have an increased risk of HZ, malignancies (excluding NMSC), and NMSC versus similarly treated younger patients, consistent with findings from the general population. Across al age groups, tofacitinib demonstrated greater efficacy than placebo as an induction and maintenance therapy.  registration numbers NCT00787202;  NCT01465763;  NCT01458951;  NCT01458574;  NCT01470612.
